<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink122">
<l>kaṇṭiku mallamō koṇkaniṉ kēḷē</l>
<l>yoḷḷiḻai yuyarmaṇal vīḻnteṉa</l>
<l>veḷḷāṅ kurukai viṉavu vōḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen your friend, haven't we, oh man from the maritime tract?</l>
<l>She who asked the white wader, because of having dropped</l>
<l>Her bright jewels in the raised sands?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
